reviewText: A very nice movie, good animation. The kids loved it.
My three year old buddy loved these movies.
I love these movies.  Widescreen presentation of all movies.

My 6-year-old son LOVES this movie.  My husband and I have seen it a few times with him, and we never get tired of it.  It is funny, meaningful, and unpredictable. I recommend this to people of all age.  I think everyone will find things they enjoy in this film.
